NSFnet Internet Statistics

Georgia Institute of Technology's Graphics, Visualization, and Usability Center has an excellent presentation of NSFNET Statistics. From that source, here are UCI local copies of graphs showing
  • log(byte_count) by service/protocol, 12/92-12/94.
  • log(packet_count) by service/protocol, 12/92-12/94.
  • Both of the above graphs, side by side.
